{"tid":477595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫中國下架VPN遭批 蘋果：為了推動言論自由","createTime":"2017-11-23T07:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T16:54:09.000Z","uid":75969,"like":5,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fac7d3dcec1c91790842b7263542b7827e20a374","tid":477595,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpIckTrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpIckTrx.jpg&h=b82af9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">蘋果在8月將VPN相關程式從APP STORE中下架，引發批評，蘋果辯稱，這能使公司繼續留在中國，推動言論自由等基本權益。（歐新社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕為阻人民「翻牆」，中國政府近來大動作掃蕩VPN（私人虛擬網路）阻人民翻牆，就連蘋果（Apple）也在8月將相關程式從APP STORE中下架，引發批評，蘋果辯稱，這能使公司可繼續留在中國，才能推動言論自由等基本權益。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體導，蘋果在今年8月屈服於中國壓力，以中國政府明令VPN開發商所提供的翻牆軟體必須取得政府許可為由，將「不符合此新規定」的app下架，引發外界質疑，認為蘋果成為中國限制網路自由的幫兇，美國友台參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）與曾在蝙蝠俠電影《黑暗騎士》客串過的民主黨籍參議員雷希（Patrick Leahy）聯名致信蘋果質疑該決策。<br />\n<br />\n這兩名美國參議員認為，中國網路長城對中國人民的威脅不亞於28年前柏林圍牆對東德人民的威脅，強調只要網路長城在的一天，中國的網路自由就處於風險中。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果對此則回應，這樣做能讓公司在中國立足「有助促進開放思想和訊息自由流動」</span>，<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公共政策副總裁霍肯（Cynthia Hogan）表示：「儘管Apple可能不同意某些國家的法律，但這樣做，能讓更好地推動包括參言論自由等基本權益。」<br />\n<br />\n蘋果執行長庫克也曾辯稱：「我們當然不想移除那些APP，但就像我們在其他國家的作法一樣，無論我們在哪裡做生意，都要遵守該國的法律。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2262219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2262219&d=VT7FvYTkX2N6WbAcYSLOrL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=c6682f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2262219&h=f828c578\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2262219</a>"},{"pid":"a565dc015aa882d6fd1bd468339739333efc9cd4","tid":477595,"uid":45788,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"想賣iphone就賣iphone啦<br />\n<br />\n用宣揚言論自由做擋箭牌，扮到自己好慘咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78420faf05a7bd568b44cea1416ff4c8548aae15","tid":477595,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"曲線？"},{"pid":"641cb2c409f9e3fdeb8090b3204eda98ae7b06d1","tid":477595,"uid":97080,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"個iOS 自由到未?"},{"pid":"9b925f859c07a5aeee8b03c0003f8a8ce2d54e96","tid":477595,"uid":6752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"鎖死班賤種唔好咩"},{"pid":"dcbf77f386dcdb4a444e0125447f8c2e66b37969","tid":477595,"uid":5159,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好放佢地出黎"},{"pid":"b82bc644dfaafa4a0c34d50cdf6ffcc092068790","tid":477595,"uid":120859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"a sense of pride and accomplishment"},{"pid":"37fa4e2117a5a17556bac472c230cb8132f9bf55","tid":477595,"uid":19353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"我殺人都係為左救人咋"},{"pid":"9a5829e6979c5adc951aab8d56be63436b1454df","tid":477595,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"中國邏輯出現了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8548ad2a905c7c9e5fbecf16989689166c3de28","tid":477595,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚愛國又要用美帝資本主義嘅產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c727a1f7672aa2ad87d84a0541937f3cfab766e","tid":477595,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d